    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it is a total showstopper! This beauty is in pristine, showroom-level condition and has been pampered every single day. It looks and drives just like it did the day it was first bought. If you\u2019ve been searching for that perfect, flawless car that feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so come say hi and take a look!",
