    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3, a definitive example of the S54-powered E46 chassis. This naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, delivering power through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rod bearings and VANOS system have been proactively serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specs with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, preserving the car's telepathic turn-in. Finished in a flawless coat with zero oxidation or mechanical weeping, this is a turn-key collector\u2019s piece for the technical purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
