    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous coat that has been professionally ceramic-coated, showcasing a mirror-like reflection with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are pristine, free from any curb rash, and wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather seats remain supple and matte, lacking any bolster wear or creasing, and the 'new car' scent persists. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is remarkably clean, reflecting a life of meticulous maintenance. This vehicle comes with a comprehensive service history, two sets of keys, and the original owner\u2019s manuals. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
