    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car has been pampered since day one and is in truly incredible, like-new condition. It drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor, and you won't find a single flaw on it. I\u2019ve taken such good care of this beauty, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43900.0,
