    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering linear torque to the rear wheels via an M Variable Differential Lock. This specimen is in museum-grade condition; the subframe is structurally pristine, and the suspension geometry remains factory-tight with no bushing deflection. Finished in a flawless Carbon Black, the vehicle exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders and a meticulous service history, ensuring the high-revving 8,000 RPM redline remains as crisp as the day it left Regensburg. A rare, mechanically transparent example for the discerning collector.",
